0 = Phonecall (Telephone voive)
1 = Speech Recognition active (SDS active e.g. voice prompts)
2 = Emergency Call
3 = beep-signal (Signal tone)
4 = Operator Call
5 = Ringing
6 = Phonecall wideband voice
    (e.g. UMTS min 100H";
