1 = PIN was accepted by the SIM-card.";
CM_ SG_ 1637 TF_Phone_RegistrationState "Network registration status: 
set field to exact value from +CREG. In 
case +CREG returns ERROR (or until first 
OK response comes after init bit switches 
to 0), set it to 7. 
0 = no service, not searching 
1 = registered at home network 
2 = no s";
CM_ SG_ 1637 TF_Phone_ring "Incoming or waiting call 
0 = phone does not ring  
1 = phone rings ";
CM_ SG_ 1637 TF_Phone_SIM_ok "State of the SIM card reader
0 = Telephone can not recognize SIM-card or no SIM-card inserted. 
1 = Telephone has detected the SIM card.";
CM_ SG_ 1637 TF_Phone_Status "Anrufstatus
